title.narrative: Cambodia Relief, Recovery and Resilience Development Policy Financing

description.narrative: The program development objective is to support the Royal Government of Cambodia to effectively deal with the COVID-19 crisis and its aftermath by: (i) continuing to provide timely and targeted relief to the affected population; (ii) facilitating robust recovery through structural reforms; and (iii) building resilience against future economic shocks.
